# ============================================================================
# MongoDB Users and Databases Configuration
# ============================================================================
# Format: username:password_env_var:database:roles
# Roles: readWrite, dbAdmin, userAdmin (comma-separated)
#
# Lines starting with # are comments and will be ignored
#
# Environment-based activation:
#   - local-dev: all uncommented users (MongoDB not shared)
#   - stage/prod: all uncommented users
#
# Only add users for microservices that actually exist in your project
# ============================================================================

# Example db users - REMOVE these lines if you don't use these services
# user-service:USER_SERVICE_MONGO_PASSWORD:user_service_db:readWrite,dbAdmin
# recipe-service:RECIPE_SERVICE_MONGO_PASSWORD:recipe_service_db:readWrite
